{"tid":386243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界好多人都誤解咗內向嘅人","createTime":"2017-09-03T17:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:27.000Z","uid":143241,"like":112,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b116e89b3911ddd698688a97771e0ae7e0befd31","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"内向嘅人不過係鍾意獨處嘅時候多過外向嘅人啫,你哋外向嘅人一聚埋就嘈到拆天咁,有冇諗過係你哋個圈外嘅人個感受啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我同你哋一齊聚會,我一個人坐喺道唔多出聲木口木面咁就問我發生咩事,問我做咩唔講嘢,其實我唔係唔想講.但你哋啲話題咁無聊我實在無辦法可以keeping同你哋講落去,嚟嚟去去都係飲飲食食咩波鞋明星乜乜柒柒咁,你想我點撘嗲啊.其實坐埋一齊傾下哲學論盡時政唔得嘅咩？<br />\n老老實實,其實有時出嚟聚下當個聚會完結番到屋企就會覺得好攰,嗰種攰係仲辛苦過番工........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明呢個世界有三分之一嘅人都係內向,即係三個有一個係,但點解無論喺邊道都好似冇咁嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add6c7a13aa87b0346966a5d91b8a302bc90cdc8","tid":386243,"uid":5921,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"內向都有唔同程度....<br />\n當佢內向過你 你就係外向個班....<br />\n所以都係搵返同level既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b938546075cf19b47aaabc80ea85ffab7acd58f","tid":386243,"uid":61327,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:27:48.000Z","msg":"發覺外向既人多數都好偽君子"},{"pid":"f9aed84ac1a3290c767b0a30bdaffba7419b0d05","tid":386243,"uid":56795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"我內向到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489681ddb9f6c57e899fb5cd177f1be4115bd66e","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺外向既人多數都好偽君子</blockquote><br />\n我都覺,同埋佢哋多數都幾口花"},{"pid":"c5f3e4b4d610c526708ffdcceda2717e12ad2098","tid":386243,"uid":36443,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"我都係，明明同一個圈子，識既時間都差唔多 但佢地就變得好熟，而我，好似永遠隔左道牆<br />\n同佢地一齊就會變得唔似自己，變唔出聲既毒撚<br />\n改唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76859441068f639694590a5130771fee5c81e203","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我內向到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實作為一個內向嘅人,我發覺到就算冇朋友都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128e7c599c549fe191d419bf5f18dacf0f8c6dba","tid":386243,"uid":105445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"放左工都鐘意自己一個人去飲茶飲咖啡 唔想埋人堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9510180288816b958e4eaa0562ecab096296316","tid":386243,"uid":78252,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"你段野似唔啱channel無野講多過關內向外向事wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外向都可以熱烈討論有營養話題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f766b2f218156ff774a9b2e473e87981389a01e","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你段野似唔啱channel無野講多過關內向外向事wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外向都可以熱烈討論有營養話題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者係我表達得唔夠好喇,其實我係可以完全唔同人傾計都冇問題"},{"pid":"f1e09bf6db37739f25cb981f68ea743279630075","tid":386243,"uid":102978,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"我好明白出席完大型聚會 返到屋企會好攰果種心情...<br />\n作為內向既人比較鍾意獨處/2人世界/3-4人小聚會<br />\n咁會自在啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de43385dc81440e99d57a0d5aeef7e408c92733","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好明白出席完大型聚會 返到屋企會好攰果種心情...<br />\n作為內向既人比較鍾意獨處/2人世界/3-4人小聚會<br />\n咁會自在啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實對我嚟講兩個人已經好夠,頂盡4個夠曬數"},{"pid":"15bf41b1331a35642876ffb8882f1fe6f4a63454","tid":386243,"uid":5397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"咁你可以選擇唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地問你都係怕你悶<br />\n應該唔會逼你講野。<br />\n<br />\n我自己都內向，平時聚會少出聲同埋岩玩先去。想摺既時候，就直接拒絕個邀請。<br />\n細個會特登融入d圈子，大個就自己舒服就可以。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有時聚會好多野講個d人,都未必係外向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係慣左做個個角色或者慣左要social 搞氣氛。"},{"pid":"aa7251ba3e58261257e0afb9fe3de85ae3245fad","tid":386243,"uid":82628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"外向嘅人有個好強力嘅工具，稱為語言藝術<br />\n對唔同嘅人都可以表現圓滑<br />\n內向嘅人係做唔到 就算講嘅內容意思一模一樣"},{"pid":"5dc10689cfc3907c37873e0c0ad38ae5a2450545","tid":386243,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我內向到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實作為一個內向嘅人,我發覺到就算冇朋友都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又開呢個post?"},{"pid":"37c8250b195e9605d7a1536e92d406254f7379e0","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我內向到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實作為一個內向嘅人,我發覺到就算冇朋友都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又開呢個post?</blockquote><br />\n咁呻下都得呱"},{"pid":"3fb6c7c1c8159c4418e147354062a065b3317bdd","tid":386243,"uid":28624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"內向俾社會標示為有問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解外向既人多過內向既咁多<br />\n以前每級係班中都俾人當異類 自閉仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301e732c04894efd832d1976dc36168b907bf97e","tid":386243,"uid":28112,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"毒就毒啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c1493ed7dbc9df98fc34207f5815ade0126f58","tid":386243,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒就毒啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67006950fff2143262386441bc69254dc3194a7","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內向俾社會標示為有問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解外向既人多過內向既咁多<br />\n以前每級係班中都俾人當異類 自閉仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel bro"},{"pid":"4bd1c3e4fef6d41be633151d2505baba3bd86faf","tid":386243,"uid":134335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"唔想講廢話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c5181c49fe6f62c3d9eda0d86e97118256ac06","tid":386243,"uid":23323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"自問算圓滑嘅人<br />\n一向係朋友堆中算多野講嗰堆<br />\n但係每次聚會完其實都好攰<br />\n有時放假寧願講大話話有野做都唔想出街<br />\n都唔知自己係算內向定外向"},{"pid":"abfca204e36ed8a0afcde4e0271dccaca2a745fd","tid":386243,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"所以你只可以上黎取暖"},{"pid":"c01be2db2dcf0db90b12654ced61920d5dbc4dc4","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以你只可以上黎取暖</blockquote><br />\n因為外邊個世界冇人明白我"},{"pid":"0d75339e68c1902e04d90438bc12df043e3560d8","tid":386243,"uid":90457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"智者言寡，嘈者言多"},{"pid":"66b74b1636f7e0ff949ee742c8bade653b172f3a","tid":386243,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒就毒啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知你中上樣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb9d3a497d58be30b1c798370175dad1177d268","tid":386243,"uid":141181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"我勁內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891cf0d9d7ef7b7f593120139e2968125237d459","tid":386243,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a8ed8450d3d1b793dabd43d1a869e0bf4572df","tid":386243,"uid":114193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"內向唔一定等於唔識講野/應酬<br />\n只係我地覺得不斷同人講野好攰，好費精神啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6941012496c812a10842850b41a8941d34be35","tid":386243,"uid":9863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"我唔講嘢又得 多嘢講又得<br />\n講啲飲飲食食垃圾話題又得<br />\n認真有營養有深度嘅都得<br />\n我講咩就取決於人地咩模式講嘢<br />\n同埋 熟嘅咪可以傾深入啲<br />\n唔熟嘅傾吃喝玩樂都好正常<br />\n咁算內向定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 有得揀會傾有營養嘅嘢"},{"pid":"39901e739675e46adb344224e67ac60e8e43178f","tid":386243,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37198267fda93d13f91e39c6346e4693b4073d6e","tid":386243,"uid":59387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c70b7eba627c16ac1e3c74bb993f004c065d4b","tid":386243,"uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"好識social 可以同任何人都好好吹<br />\n但其實每次都覺得好攰 只係想靜靜地諗下野"},{"pid":"76c0d2ca200d71337f4a5dbe7b78362e971e46f2","tid":386243,"uid":31650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"可以試下睇d關於社交or人際關係的書<br />\n應該可以比到幫助or靈感你地改善個情況<br />\n有陣時內向定外向係睇你有冇技巧去從社交攞到滿足感"},{"pid":"f85c1b0a03ceacc93c5e1de71c80699563b0d3fd","tid":386243,"uid":31650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以試下睇d關於社交or人際關係的書<br />\n應該可以比到幫助or靈感你地改善個情況<br />\n有陣時內向定外向係睇你有冇技巧去從社交攞到滿足感</blockquote><br />\n例子：自己睇緊 好似有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09eaca0f12d63062aad6aef35a0ab0612ed1d76b","tid":386243,"uid":141181,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/123946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F123946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=07bbcf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/123955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F123955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45cbfc51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d3c27f344a9abdfc00a0b0fa1428930e837dca3","tid":386243,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢個世界跟本無所謂內外向<br />\n岩到頻率個個都外向啦<br />\n正如搵兩個毒撚講動漫<br />\n隨時由天光傾到夜晚都得<br />\n兩個mk講食女咪又一樣<br />\n以前講野都會特登去迎合人地<br />\n而家覺得岩頻率咪傾<br />\n唔岩咪say句hi就算<br />\n唔駛咁介懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651d22e76d097dbd4594cc81ee96a910301ce588","tid":386243,"uid":92879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"同樣係內向既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學真係可以一個朋友都冇<br />\n好在畢業之前都有識番幾個<br />\n升中之後開始識多咗人<br />\n直至中學畢業之後都仲有聯絡<br />\n<br />\n朋友真心覺得唔需要太多<br />\n自己認為足夠就可以啦"},{"pid":"3e65a078ad571555e17768f09f8cee8969e357eb","tid":386243,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/123946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F123946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=07bbcf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/123955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F123955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45cbfc51&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n全中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2ea9dde340733ed22976be6800558bfdf9b57a","tid":386243,"uid":11376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"完全同意  唔係唔鍾意圍威喂  但玩得多會攰會厭會煩"},{"pid":"36ecd84be6aa3db0fde4615de6b6bc537206f310","tid":386243,"uid":59387,"l